Haskell Raytracer
=================

This program is Copyright (C) 2006-2012 Ryan Lothian. All rights reserved.


Purpose 
-------
This program renders 3d objects using raytracing.

Visit http://www.ryanlothian.com/projects/haskell_raytracer/ for more 
information.


